{"tid":614504,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港其中一個underrated嘅本土美食一定係腸粉!!!","createTime":"2018-04-02T14:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T01:28:06.000Z","uid":136116,"like":48,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"90e03294bfb7ddf7d20df1ceb5c955f694f3fca9","tid":614504,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:55:41.000Z","msg":"其他國家真係好難複製呢個口感 呢個味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n煙韌嘅口感 帶小小米香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識食一定係加甜醬 花生醬 芝麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者入面包啲蝦仁 牛肉 叉燒 都好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係個人覺得最正一定係炸兩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個野食根本係只應天上有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱炸好嘅脆扑扑油條 出面包住一層腸粉皮 做到內脆外軟咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後再沾上啲花生醬 芝麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母 一路打字一路流撚晒口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6b9e638d937e960e821421b945b143e330e3a2","tid":614504,"uid":10793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:57:00.000Z","msg":"香港本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係廣東同潮州咩"},{"